{"id":161,"date":"2014-06-20T01:57:37","date_gmt":"2014-06-20T01:57:37","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/coastcaritas.wordpress.com\/?p=161"},"modified":"2020-10-26T15:50:59","modified_gmt":"2020-10-26T20:50:59","slug":"heart-and-cross-pins-for-sale","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/2014\/06\/20\/heart-and-cross-pins-for-sale\/","title":{"rendered":"*Sold Out* &#8211; Heart and Cross Pins for Sale"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-161 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/20140619_202611.jpg'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/20140619_202611-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/20140619_202611-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/20140619_202611-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/><\/a>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/20140619_203801.jpg'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/20140619_203801-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/20140619_203801-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/20140619_203801-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/><\/a>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/20140619_202757.jpg'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/20140619_202757-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/20140619_202757-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/20140619_202757-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/><\/a>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/figure>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n<p>I wanted to find a nice red lapel pin of the heart and cross, but did not have any success. I decided to create a design and have them made.<\/p>\n<p>I would like to make the extra pins available for sale. They are cloisonne enamel with a nickel border and a polished finish. The color is a true red&#8211;the color you see on the jacket photo is more accurate than the close up.The back is a standard military clutch. They are 0.75in\/1.9cm tall. They look especially nice on a jacket lapel, ballcap, or bag.<\/p>\n<p>They are available for $6.50 for the first pin, $4.00 for each additional pin (the cost includes shipping within the United States &#8211; we can work out something if you&#8217;re outside the US). Please send me a message through this site if you&#8217;d like to order one or more!<\/p>\n<p><em>The pins are sold out. I will update this page in the future if I get more. I am including the original design image should anyone wish to use it, gratis:<\/em><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/pin.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-725\" src=\"http:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/pin.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"898\" height=\"1136\" srcset=\"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/pin.jpg 898w, https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/pin-237x300.jpg 237w, https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/pin-768x972.jpg 768w, https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/06\/pin-809x1024.jpg 809w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 898px) 100vw, 898px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>I wanted to find a nice red lapel pin of the heart and cross, but did not have any success. I decided to create a design and have them made. I would like to make the extra pins available for sale. They are cloisonne enamel with a nickel border and a polished finish. The color [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":160,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"image","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/161"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=161"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/161\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":850,"href":"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/161\/revisions\/850"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/160"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=161"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=161"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/coastcaritas.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=161"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}